----------------
  nsfw-service
----------------

[ Usage ]

Send a HTTP Request to Port 9000 with the request body as your image.
This service supports the following codecs WEBP, PNG, GIF, and JPEG.
Animated images are not supported, GIFs will only use the first frame.

- Example Response Status -

500 : Tensorflow Error, parse body as plaintext
200 : Classification OK, parse body as JSON string

400: Invalid Image Data
405 : Method Not Allowed, send a request with the POST method 
411 : Failed to read Request Body
415 : Unsupported Image Type 
422 : Invalid Image Dimensions ( >2048px / <32px )

- Example Response Body -

{
   "allowed":true,
   "image":{
      "height":400,
      "width":400
   },
   "logits":{
      "drawing":0.6907269,
      "hentai":0.226651,
      "neutral":0.08234569,
      "porn":0.0002462058,
      "sexy":0.000030217838
   },
   "timings":{
      "classify":16636400,
      "decode":4752600,
      "probe":7965500
   }
}

